title.Value: Insane Road Race Nissan B13 @ CCCPR Track Time 2nd track visit

description.Name: description
description.Value:
CCCPR 5/19/2013 Track Time @ Salinas Speedway P.R.

2ND visit of the car to a track...now in a different one Salinas Speedway where we tested the car and had some fun with it....next visits should be better since we know a bit more about the track.
